New Records: Matt Olson tied the Braves' single-season record with his 51st home run of 2023, matching the mark set by Andruw Jones in 2005.
Key Match Events: Matt Olson hit his 51st home run of the season against Philadelphia Phillies right-hander Zack Wheeler in the top of the fourth inning, tying the game 1-1.
Atlanta Braves won the game 7-6 in 10 innings.
